tiers.ability_description: Light Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Light Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain a buff, they recover 2% Health and Protection.
Whenever Empire allies critically hit an enemy during their turn, that ally gains 10% Offense (stacking) for 2 turns.
Whenever Light Side allies gain a buff, they recover 2% Health and Protection.
